Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.87,0:02:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是对嗓子很管用的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.38,0:02:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这… 这不是很合理的东西嘛！！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.00,0:02:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说的话太不够现实感了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.17,0:02:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之 一定要先让他相信！！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.88,0:02:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.25,0:03:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只是单纯的喉咙痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.35,0:03:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.14,0:03:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说被谁绞着脖子好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.18,0:03:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同时好像还突然出现怪声…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.14,0:03:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直说就是像被附身似的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.10,0:03:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是… 那么回事吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你看太多奇怪的书了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.48,0:03:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有点 病了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.49,0:03:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到他竟会说出这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.41,0:03:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将本职…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.90,0:03:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.48,0:03:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这位住持 真的相信灵吗！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.09,0:03:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是好不容易都来了寺院
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.87,0:03:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能就这么漫不经心的回去了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.46,0:03:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脖子被什么可怕的东西胡乱的掐住了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.01,0:03:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失礼！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被看穿了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.69,0:03:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.94,0:04:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凭这半吊子的演技来跟他的本质抗衡 本就是我的错误！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.90,0:04:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得拿出真正的气魄给他看…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.94,0:04:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要让他相信——
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.95,0:04:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就要尽全力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挥棒！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.12,0:04:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎… 怎么回事！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.63,0:04:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说… 你在干什么！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.40,0:04:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在干什么！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.01,0:04:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在干什么！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.14,0:04:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你 你这混蛋！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.79,0:04:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.62,0:04:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.08,0:05:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要对老夫的寺庙…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.67,0:05:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要对老夫的寺庙…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.17,0:05:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做些什么！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.76,0:05:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的梦想是将来做一个科学家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟 糟了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.72,0:05:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有点太失控了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.60,0:05:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用科学证明这世界上的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.90,0:05:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能够让很多人都理解那些
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后等时机成熟就说出我唯一想传达的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.12,0:05:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.53,0:05:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快 快给我滚！ 你这个恶灵！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.45,0:05:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人总是能变成恶灵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.55,0:05:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有破绽！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.85,0:05:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.31,0:05:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美星 好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.97,0:06:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出现啦！！ 长野原前辈！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.77,0:06:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这段没见到的时间里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.15,0:06:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美星也成中学生啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.49,0:06:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因为你最近完全不来道场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.91,0:06:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近 大学那边的练习也没去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.91,0:06:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翘掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.91,0:06:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那还能在这期间获得全日本冠军哦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.91,0:06:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个可恶的天才型选手！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.13,0:06:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在要去道场？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.54,0:06:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 刚才社团活动结束现在过去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.09,0:06:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长野原前辈要来么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.80,0:06:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是那种 练习太多会变弱的类型啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乱说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.72,0:06:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…你个天才型选手！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.81,0:06:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我承认她确实很强
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.48,0:06:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我不能接受的是 明明没怎么练习还那么强的事实
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.94,0:06:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长野原前辈初中一年级的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.23,0:06:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与大师兄对决的时候还得了一分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.49,0:06:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个大师兄哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.95,0:06:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同样身为初中生的我完全达不到那水平…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.62,0:07:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明我在社团活动结束后就去道场
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连假日都不休息全用来练习！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.50,0:07:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大师兄也说过“只要努力大门一定会开启”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.46,0:07:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 黑猫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.31,0:07:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦诶 小猫咪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.34,0:07:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一看到这个人就会动摇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.43,0:07:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…就试着砍她一刀…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.99,0:07:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一刀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.02,0:07:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种情况的话 我也行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.44,0:07:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然现在只能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.73,0:07:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天与她一决高下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.78,0:07:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且 总有一天连大师兄也！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.07,0:07:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个天才型选手！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱… 抱歉！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大师兄！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.25,0:07:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\c&HD6A6FE&\pos(622,498)}与爱有关的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.14,0:08:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.94,0:08:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听好啊 要好好做哦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.44,0:08:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸想让我来继任第二代啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.11,0:08:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个和这个气球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.99,0:08:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是有小孩来的话就给他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.70,0:08:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不会吃你这一套哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.16,0:08:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有机会我就逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.21,0:08:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这气球…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.58,0:08:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没飘起来——！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.43,0:08:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,900)\pos(652,493)\c&H0A0A0A&\shad0\bord0\K100}只{\K100}言{\K100}片{\K100}语
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.52,0:08:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后的最后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.15,0:08:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总是希望能有一个还算完美的结局
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.58,0:09:06.08,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45\fad(700,0)\pos(150,360)\shad2\4c&H10110F&\c&HEBF9F8&}某\N个\N圣\N诞\N的\N单\N幅\N漫\N画
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.58,0:09:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士要向圣诞老人许什么愿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.66,0:09:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有巧克力的点心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有彩色铅笔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.96,0:09:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有蛋糕做的橡皮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.71,0:09:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有… 还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.34,0:09:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然这么多 真狡猾！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.26,0:09:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 那 我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.51,0:09:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两袋鸡蛋和
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,500克牛肉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.10,0:09:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有伊万比利宾的书…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.10,0:09:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs30}伊万比利宾（1876.8.16-1942.2.7）：俄罗斯的画家、插画家和舞台艺术设计师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.68,0:09:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士已经先要了很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.31,0:09:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名乃只能要一个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.61,0:09:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.40,0:09:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有点稍微多了 所以没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.28,0:09:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个也借给你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.05,0:09:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.21,0:10:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 圣诞老人啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.07,0:10:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.39,0:10:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45\c&H73DB83&\3c&H333838&\bord2\shad0\frz10.122\pos(478,362)}好吃的菠萝包
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.49,0:10:28.49,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(1200,360)}陷\N阱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.54,0:10:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才没空跟你玩这种把戏呢！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赶快把这个面具摘掉… 掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.68,0:10:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.59,0:10:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好疼疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.63,0:10:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要逃吗 刚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.13,0:10:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.09,0:10:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这回在面具上动了点手脚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.28,0:10:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手脚…！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.39,0:10:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个面具的里面啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.06,0:10:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,涂了 油漆啦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.53,0:11:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好烫！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.24,0:11:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟啦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.04,0:11:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,速攻肉包子掉啦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.25,0:11:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一口都没吃上呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.16,0:11:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛嘛 薇波希
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.62,0:11:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是这肉包子里有毒的话薇波希就死了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.46,0:11:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反过来说挺好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.96,0:11:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不好哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.67,0:11:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放学最大的一个乐趣就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.97,0:11:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事情都是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.14,0:11:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一个乐观的心态的话就会发生好事的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.68,0:11:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向掉了的肉包子 说声感谢☆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.77,0:11:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 你这份乐观心态
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.19,0:11:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经决定了今后不管遇到什么样的情况都要乐观看待！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.74,0:11:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看你看 把脏了的地方弄掉的话还能吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.74,0:11:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有毒的设定消失的真快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.30,0:11:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.36,0:11:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把底下的皮撕开的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.36,0:11:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好烫！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.84,0:11:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪糕安全！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.00,0:12:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看你看！！幸运会降临在乐观的人身上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.42,0:12:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是总要乐观魔法！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.09,0:12:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包子还是出局了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.22,0:12:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦 这种时候也要乐观些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.09,0:12:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是这肉包子里有毒的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.43,0:12:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,薇波希就死了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.56,0:12:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变化好少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.43,0:12:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算脏的地方弄掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.31,0:12:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,碰上雪糕的地方我也忍不了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.44,0:12:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦 要乐观要乐观
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.15,0:12:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老天啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.32,0:12:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为刚才的包子太热所以化了一点吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.74,0:12:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想想要是雪糕有毒的话 这点程度…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.74,0:12:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才不是吃的挺爽的吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.91,0:12:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.54,0:12:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45\shad0\bord1\c&H8D9297&\3c&H78848A&\frz25.247\pos(736,242)}没\N中\N奖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.25,0:12:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乐观效果连续没中嘛！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.59,0:12:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 这是上帝的不要连续吃两根弄坏了肚子的启示啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.13,0:12:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天让我见识了小菲式的顽强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.88,0:12:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且这个雪糕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.22,0:12:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽说里面奶油的夹心已经完全出局了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.68,0:12:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外面的冰的部分 洗洗的话脏东西就没了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.85,0:12:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对那些部分 要感谢啊☆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.64,0:13:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那雪糕你还想吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.98,0:13:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等——
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.96,0:13:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.43,0:13:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.64,0:13:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉全都湿了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.23,0:13:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 小菲！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.39,0:13:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要积极要积极
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.62,0:13:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我放弃啦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.29,0:14:02.13,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs75\fad(550,700)\shad2\4c&H10110F&\pos(1180,360)\c&HFEFEFE&}向\N自\N由\N狂\N奔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.37,0:14:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要是那么不想继任第二代的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.75,0:14:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今后还会有第二第三个陷阱的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.97,0:14:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.31,0:14:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.64,0:14:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.98,0:14:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.77,0:14:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.90,0:14:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答案啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.66,0:14:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立花 你毕业后准备做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.41,0:14:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还在犹豫去上大学还是去上烹饪学校
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.29,0:14:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烹饪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.88,0:14:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.84,0:14:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什什什什什什…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:14:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嫁给他？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.18,0:15:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点 立花
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.81,0:15:04.35,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60\fscx95\pos(1095,150)}雪\N飘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.81,0:15:04.35,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial\fs18\pos(1148,150)}flsnow
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.77,0:15:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像这样系起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.94,0:15:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样就好了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.32,0:15:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回来啦——
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.57,0:15:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 名乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.69,0:15:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟阪本出去散会步
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.15,0:15:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过一会有朋友过来学习 可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.57,0:15:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.32,0:15:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士也出去玩 一会就回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.25,0:15:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 我们走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.84,0:15:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.54,0:15:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦诶我说！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.23,0:15:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么 小鬼！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.20,0:15:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要死了 要死了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.80,0:15:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.59,0:15:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我听你的愿望！！ 你的愿望是什么！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.59,0:15:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想要什么！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.64,0:15:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鲨鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.30,0:15:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个人在～默默哭泣～～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.18,0:15:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要哭的是我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.69,0:15:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了！！鲨鱼是吧！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.02,0:15:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小事一桩啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.27,0:15:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很快就会给你准备的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.61,0:15:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧给我松开混蛋！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.66,0:15:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狗啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.95,0:16:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是狗的话 说不定会被咬…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.99,0:16:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阪本 是狗啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.58,0:16:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说不定会被咬…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.33,0:16:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为为为 为什么要怕狗什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.75,0:16:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有 有绳子呢 不会被咬的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.97,0:16:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 只能逃了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.68,0:16:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 快跑吧！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.10,0:16:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阪本！！跑不了了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.81,0:16:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要放弃！！ 放弃的话就完了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.18,0:16:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟主人说 让她赶快系上绳子！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.56,0:16:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这下…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.19,0:16:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.36,0:16:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋啦完蛋啦！！赶快竭尽全力想啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.48,0:16:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么招么？有什么招么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.53,0:16:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么招么…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.36,0:16:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兜里面有块软糖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.22,0:16:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就它了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.99,0:16:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁它们吃的时候赶紧跑！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.25,0:16:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了！你赶紧做点什么逃跑用的道具！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.71,0:16:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对啊！差点忘了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.35,0:16:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阪本！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.13,0:16:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.05,0:16:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有做道具用的道具！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.35,0:17:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.84,0:17:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然到了这步田地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.93,0:17:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要煮要烤随你便吧！ 这群混蛋！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.85,0:17:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要煮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.52,0:17:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要烤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.52,0:17:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随你便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.77,0:17:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,款待一番
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.07,0:17:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要被吃了 要被吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.48,0:17:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被吃的话 可能就被吃了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.53,0:17:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧？ 博士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.58,0:17:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么在哭啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.83,0:17:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迷路了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.66,0:17:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是小佑！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.20,0:17:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子就是之前说的博士吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.58,0:17:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦！ 阪本也一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.21,0:17:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我摸摸让我摸摸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.96,0:17:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是哦小佑！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.96,0:17:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干掉那两条狗！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.71,0:17:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比想像得更加唰啦唰啦的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.71,0:17:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想来～～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.88,0:17:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少开玩笑了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.38,0:17:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快干掉那两条狗！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.64,0:17:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.47,0:17:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被咬了所以想要报仇是吧！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.39,0:17:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是啊！！马上要被咬了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.64,0:17:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.48,0:17:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来是怕狗啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.98,0:17:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是小鬼Q太郎吗！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.98,0:17:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs30}译注：Q太郎很怕狗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.89,0:17:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是哦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.77,0:17:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看那是狗啊 会咬的！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.56,0:17:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看看嘛 明明这么老实才不会被咬的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.32,0:17:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会咬的！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.23,0:17:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会咬的——
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.32,0:18:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会——咬！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.15,0:18:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要吃口香糖么？什么哒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.15,0:18:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs30}译注：口香糖{\fnＤＦブラッシュＲＤW7\fs26}（ガム）{\r\fs30}与咬{\fnＤＦブラッシュＲＤW7\fs26}（啮む）{\r\fs30}音近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.16,0:18:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会——咬——的——！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.74,0:18:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那咱们试试？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.33,0:18:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来 伸手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说小佑… 没事吧！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.39,0:18:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\c&H2D343B&\bord0\shad2\pos(90,102)\4c&HFFFFFF&}咬了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.27,0:18:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不接近的话就不会被咬的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.31,0:18:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以没关系啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.69,0:18:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小佑被… 小佑被…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.29,0:18:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 小佑是笨蛋嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.28,0:18:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.24,0:18:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.78,0:18:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.57,0:18:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把小佑叫起来 我们一起去名乃家吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.28,0:18:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶—— 你知道名乃么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然知
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.11,0:19:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.15,0:19:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好好拉着绳子的话可是不行的！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.33,0:19:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟它们玩了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.24,0:19:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.29,0:19:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会被咬的！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.84,0:19:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.34,0:19:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鲨鱼巧克力！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.55,0:19:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多谢你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.26,0:19:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又拿到巧克力了狗又走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.31,0:19:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好啦 阪本
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.89,0:19:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼 连狗都害怕你不过是个小孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.44,0:19:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起那个 赶紧给我把绳子拿下来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.77,0:20:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿到巧克力了 所以可以哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.06,0:20:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…啊咧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.07,0:20:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.07,0:20:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阪本给我拿下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.70,0:20:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好紧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.11,0:20:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要能拿下来的话早拿了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.82,0:20:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让小佑帮我拿下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.91,0:20:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呐 小佑 帮我拿下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.29,0:20:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呐 小佑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.50,0:20:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呐小佑 我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.75,0:20:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…哦诶 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.82,0:20:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.15,0:20:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好多狗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.70,0:20:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好多汗啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.53,0:20:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了 拿到巧克力了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.99,0:21:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.23,0:21:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}鲨鱼巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.50,0:21:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来相生同学和长野原同学好慢啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.31,0:21:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}巧克力巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.85,0:21:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}鲨鱼鲨鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.05,0:21:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs45}鲨鱼的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.81,0:21:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是朝这边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.81,0:21:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这… 这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.40,0:21:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕蒂… 小帕蒂…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.02,0:21:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底做了什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.32,0:21:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.07,0:21:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人活着 是要互相说明的 贵志
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.16,0:21:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动物们也一样是这种心情的 贵志
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.12,0:21:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小瞧动物和人之间的羁绊可是不行的哦 贵志
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.09,0:21:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.89,0:21:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是淳志
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.25,0:22:29.63,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}仰げば尊し　我が師の恩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.25,0:22:29.63,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}翘首瞻仰 无尽珍藏 吾师恩情浩荡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.95,0:22:45.72,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}教えの庭にも　はや幾年
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.95,0:22:45.72,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}校园操场 书声琅琅 几年飞逝如光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.75,0:23:03.57,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}思えばいと疾し　この年月
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.75,0:23:03.57,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}如今回想 光阴似箭 斑驳几面砖墙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.51,0:23:22.82,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}今こそ別れめ　いざさらば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.51,0:23:22.82,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}今宵一别 无尽惆怅 愿君莫相忘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.77,0:23:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是菠萝包
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.02,0:23:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人类啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.30,0:23:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是有蜜瓜的味道好 还是没有好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.15,0:23:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将议论永远继续下去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.86,0:23:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一话的日常是第二十三话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.57,0:23:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敬请期待！
